1.Download Raspbian ---from latest version available on the website, https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/

2.Unzip the compressed image --Using Unzip 

3.The disk image has to be written on the microSD Card ---Done using Etcher 

4.Insert the sd card in pi and boot up, ---plugin with a supply

5. By default, 
Username, --pi
Password, --raspberry
